stories.title: Sri Lanka v Bangladesh
stories.subTitle: Second one-day international
stories.summary: At Sinhalese Sports Club, Colombo, August 5

stories.title: Bangladesh slump to humiliating defeat
stories.summary: On Sunday Bangladesh had pointed to a brighter future with a respectable performance, but on Monday they reinforced their reputation as international minnows, as they were bowled out for a humiliating 76 at the Sinhalese Sports Club
